name: 2021 Masters
description: The Masters is the season-opening event of the 2021-22 Pinty's Grand Slam of Curling season with 16 of the top men's teams and 16 of the top women's teams from around the world. The preliminary round features a triple knockout format with eight teams in both divisions qualifying for the playoffs.
